《Wii Sports》在业内批评界同样获得了广泛肯定。<ref name="Meta">{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/wii/wiisports|publisher=Metacritic|title=Wii Sports (Wii: 2006) Reviews|accessdate=2008-01-31|language=en|archive-date=2010-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100216183757/http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/wii/wiisports}}</ref><ref name="GameRank">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/htmlpages2/933010.asp|title=Wii Sports at Game Rankings|publisher=Game Rankings|accessdate=2018-03-11|language=en|archive-date=2009-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090203193740/http://www.gamerankings.com/htmlpages2/933010.asp}}</ref>[[GameTrailers|GameTrailers]]称其为Wii的良好补充，并称赞这五个游戏组成了一个“上佳合集”。评论称游戏为长时间玩家提供了足够的游戏性，却又会不使新手望而却步。不过GameTrailers认为，缺少竞赛模式是游戏一大缺陷，若不是随机附赠，不太值得推荐购买。<ref name="GameTrailers" />《[[GamePro|GamePro]]》同样肯定了Wii Sports随Wii免费附赠的做法。<ref name="GamePro" />[[IGN|IGN]]称其是“任天堂新硬件的成功展示”，并深享引入Wii而带来的乐趣。<ref name="ign" />[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]则称赞了游戏多人模式和健康测试功能。<ref name="GameSpot">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/wii/sports/wiisports/review.html|title=Wii Sports for Wii Review|publisher=GameSpot|last=Davis|first=Ryan|date=2006-11-19|accessdate=2008-01-31|language=en|archive-date=2011-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111031233659/http://www.gamespot.com/wii/sports/wiisports/review.html}}</ref>媒体评测一致肯定了游戏操作的易用性：IGN称其为直观的“革命性”操作方式；<ref name="ign" />《GamePro》亦表达了类似看法，赞扬其简易而拟真的运动控制。不过，GameSpot也评论说运动控制有时会飘忽不定。<ref name="GamePro" /><ref name="GameSpot" />游戏的负面评价则集中在画面和各个游戏的缺乏深度上。IGN表示游戏“在画面和深度上显得肤浅”，并评价其画面“一般”、“过时”。<ref name="ign" />其他媒体也认为其画面表现与任天堂上世代游戏机[[任天堂GameCube|GameCube]]和[[任天堂64|任天堂64]]相较并无进步 。<ref name="GamePro" /><ref name="GameTrailers" />GameSpot批评各运动项目被过度简化，GamePro也评价各项与一般的[[体育类游戏|体育类游戏]]相比显得深度不足。<ref name="GamePro" /><ref name="GameSpot" />

游戏中各项目得到的评价也各有不同。IGN认为保龄球、网球和棒球游戏很“有趣迷人”，而[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]则觉得与网球和保龄球相比，棒球、高尔夫球和拳击缺乏深入的游戏性。<ref name="ign" /><ref name="EuroG">{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/article.php?article_id=70561|title=Wii Sports Review|last=Bramwell|first=Tom|publisher=Eurogamer|date=2006-11-30|accessdate=2008-02-01|language=en|archive-date=2007-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071015221126/http://www.eurogamer.net/article.php?article_id=70561}}</ref>身为一名保龄球迷的《PC Magazine》专栏作家约翰·C·德沃夏克对保龄球游戏的拟真物理作用大加赞赏，并表示“任天堂做了杰出的程序编写工作”。他肯定了加入体力活动的游戏方式，但也抱怨道长期使用会造成手腕和肩膀疼痛。<ref>{{cite web|author=Dvorak, John|url=http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,1895,2098845,00.asp|publisher=PC Magazine|title=Ode to the Wii|date=2007-03-06|accessdate=2007-05-01|language=en|archive-date=2008-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080725232014/http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,1895,2098845,00.asp}}</ref>IGN也把保龄球评为五个游戏中最佳的一项，<ref name="ign" />不过在游戏发布前，IGN就指出游戏存有可以轻易投出[[保龄球#记分方式|全中]]的漏洞，而使得游戏缺乏挑战和重複价值。<ref name="HandsOnBowling">{{cite web|url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/732/732927p1.html|title=Hands-on Wii Bowling|publisher=IGN|last=Harris|first=Craig|date=2006-09-14|accessdate=2007-05-01|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070612103515/http://wii.ign.com/articles/732/732927p1.html|archive-date=2007-06-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>但在游戏推出後，他们发现这一问题并未得到修復。<ref name="IGN-Bowling" />GameTrailers称高尔夫球游戏最具深度，但也批评在打曲线球时，游戏缺乏多路线性和控制的不可预知性。<ref name="GameTrailers" />《GamePro》同样认为高尔夫游戏内容最丰富，相较之下最为出众，但其操作却也是最难以控制的。<ref name="GamePro" />GameTrailers则是认为网球最易上手，但不满游戏发旋转球的难度过高。<ref name="GameTrailers" />IGN表示网球是最好玩的游戏之一，但缺乏移动控制却是其一大败笔。<ref name="ign" />GameTrailers认为棒球“最无价值”，因为游戏中电脑控制的防守包含运气成分过多，而将拳击视作《Wii Sports》中最佳的锻炼方式，但也批评游戏中出拳的时机太难把握。<ref name="GameTrailers" />IGN抱怨拳击游戏“简直是个苦差事”，并将其列为五个游戏中最差的项目。<ref name="ign" />

=== 获得奖项 ===

《Wii Sports》在2006年E3展的首次亮相就载誉而归，在游戏展上拿下游戏评论奖的“最佳体育游戏”。<ref>{{cite web|title=Game Critics Awards - 2006 Winners|url=http://www.gamecriticsawards.com/2006winners.html|publisher=Game Critics Awards|accessdate=2006-06-25|language=en|archive-date=2016-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414080540/http://www.gamecriticsawards.com/2006winners.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]在其“2006年E3最佳”专题中将其列为“最佳Wii游戏”和“最创新游戏”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.1up.com/do/feature?cId=3150431 |title=1UP.com's Best of E3 2006 |publisher=1UP.com |accessdate=2008-02-01 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060519214043/http://www.1up.com/do/feature?cId=3150431 |archivedate=2006-05-19 }}</ref>随着游戏的发行，《Wii Sports》更从各组织、网站和杂志斩获众多奖项。IGN授予其“2006年最佳体育游戏”，<ref>{{cite web |title=IGN.com presents The Best of 2006 - Best Sports Game |url=http://bestof.ign.com/2006/overall/16.html |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2007-01-16 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070117015534/http://bestof.ign.com/2006/overall/16.html |archivedate=2007-01-17 }}</ref>[[時代_(雜誌)|《时代》周刊]]将其列为“2006年十大电子游戏”之榜首。<ref>{{cite web|title=Top Ten Video Games of 2006|url=http://www.time.com/time/topten/2006/videogames/01.html|publisher=时代周刊|year=2006|accessdate=2006-12-25|language=en|archive-date=2007-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070109042954/http://www.time.com/time/topten/2006/videogames/01.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>《Wii Sports》还赢得了《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》2006年的“革新大赏”，<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.famitsu.com/game/news/2007/04/20/103,1177037473,70570,0,0.html| title = 速報！　ファミ通ゲームアワード2006開催！　各受賞タイトルを一挙発表！| publisher = Fami通| language = ja| date = 2007-04-20| accessdate = 2008-02-09| archive-date = 2012-10-22| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121022014632/http://www.famitsu.com/game/news/2007/04/20/103,1177037473,70570,0,0.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>《[[电子游戏月刊|电子游戏月刊]]》亦在其2006年“1Up 网络奖”中授予其“最佳多人游戏奖”。<ref>{{Citation|date=March 2007|title=EGM Presents The 2006 1UP Network Awards|periodical= Electronic Gaming Monthly|publisher=Ziff Davis|issue=213|pages=79|language = en}}</ref>在2007年[[互动成就奖|互动成就奖]]中，《Wii Sports》摘得“游戏技术杰出成就奖”、“游戏设计杰出成就奖”和“游戏杰出创新奖”三项大奖。<ref>{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100830140640/http://www.interactive.org/awards/annual_awards.asp?idAward=2007|archivedate=2010-08-30|url=http://www.interactive.org/awards/annual_awards.asp?idAward=2007|title=10th Annual Interactive Achievement Awards|publisher=Academy of Interactive Arts & Sciences|accessdate=2009-04-15|language=en|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2007年，游戏在游戏开发者优选奖（Interactive Achievement Awards）中获得“创新奖”和“最佳游戏设计奖”，<ref>{{cite web|last= Remo|first= Chris|title= Gears of War, Wii Sports, Okami Top GDC Awards|publisher= Shacknews|date= 2007-03-08|url= http://www.shacknews.com/onearticle.x/46041|accessdate= 2007-03-12|language= en|archive-date= 2010-02-27|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100227024940/http://www.shacknews.com/onearticle.x/46041}}</ref>并在日本[[文化厅媒体艺术祭|文化厅媒体艺术祭]]游戏部门上赢得“最优秀大赏”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://plaza.bunka.go.jp/english/festival/2007/ |title=Japan Media Arts Festival Award Winning Works |publisher=Japan Media Arts Plaza |accessdate=2008-01-31 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080223073426/http://plaza.bunka.go.jp/english/festival/2007/ |archivedate=2008-02-23 }}</ref>在2007年[[英国电影和电视艺术学院|英国电影和电视艺术学院]]（BAFTA）颁奖典礼上，《Wii Sports》一举囊括13项大奖中的6项：休闲游戏、游戏操作、策略与模拟游戏、运动游戏、创新游戏和多人游戏。<ref>{{cite web|url= http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/7058670.stm|publisher= BBC|title= Wii Sports dominates Bafta awards|date=2007-10-23| accessdate=2008-01-31|language = en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090427060051/http://www.bafta.org/awards/video-games/the-british-academy-video-games-awards-in-2007%2C207%2CBA.html |archivedate=2009-04-27 |url=http://www.bafta.org/awards/video-games/the-british-academy-video-games-awards-in-2007,207,BA.html |title=The British Academy Video Games Awards in 2007 |publisher=British Academy of Film and Television Arts |date=2007-10-24 |accessdate=2008-01-31 |language=en |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

== 社会影响 ==

[[File:Wii_Remote_Straps.jpg|thumb]]腕带对比（左新右旧）。]]

作为Wii在全球大获成功的一个主因，《Wii Sports》是任天堂在欧美“[[Wii系列|Wii系列]]”游戏中的第一作。<ref name="SportsSequel">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/wii/sports/wiisports/news.html?sid=6178806|title=Iwata: Wii Sports 2 benched for now|publisher=GameSpot|date=2007-09-14|accessdate=2008-02-06|language=en|archive-date=2009-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090511130221/http://www.gamespot.com/wii/sports/wiisports/news.html?sid=6178806|dead-url=no}}</ref>该系列还包括《[[第一次的Wii|第一次的Wii]]》、《[[Wii_Fit|Wii Fit]]》、《[[Wii国际象棋|Wii国际象棋]]》（Wii Chess）和《[[Wii_Music|Wii Music]]》。<ref name="WiiSeries">{{cite web| publisher=IGN| url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/766/766803p1.html| last=Casamassina| first=Matt| date=2007-02-22| title=IGN: Nintendo Lists Major Wii Games for 2007| accessdate=2007-05-01| language=en| archive-date=2007-08-08| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070808080750/http://wii.ign.com/articles/766/766803p1.html}}</ref>其续作《[[Wii運動：度假勝地|Wii運動：度假勝地]]》也於2009年内发售。<ref>{{cite web| url = http://wii.ign.com/articles/889/889659p1.html| title = E3 2008: Wii Sports Gets a Sequel| author = DeVries, Jack| publisher = IGN| date = 2008-07-15| accessdate = 2008-07-15| language = en| archive-date = 2012-01-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120118172745/http://wii.ign.com/articles/889/889659p1.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>一般认为，游戏像《Wii Fit》一样吸引了更多的休闲、女性和老人玩家，<ref name="SonyQuart">{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Technology/GadgetGuide/wireStory?id=4220585|title=Sony Quarterly Profit Rises 25 Percent|last=Kageyama|first=Yuri|publisher=ABC News|date=2008-01-31|accessdate=2008-03-10|language=en|archive-date=2008-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080918090750/http://abcnews.go.com/Technology/GadgetGuide/wireStory?id=4220585|dead-url=no}}</ref>更成为拉近家庭成员之间关系的纽带，经常使用还可作为健身和减肥的手段。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/tech/products/2007-06-17-796282832_x.htm|title=Fathers and Kids Bond Over Video Games|last=Slagle|first=Matt|date=2007-06-12|publisher=USA Today|accessdate=2008-02-05|language=en|archive-date=2009-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090609095610/http://www.usatoday.com/tech/products/2007-06-17-796282832_x.htm}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url= http://www.gamespot.com/wii/sports/wiisports/news.html?sid=6166231|title=Study: Wii kids lose weight|last=Boyes|first=Emma| publisher=GameSpot|date=2007-02-22|accessdate=2008-02-06|language = en}}</ref>利物浦约翰摩尔斯大学曾做过一项针对13-15岁青少年的研究，结果表明，玩家使用Wii时要比玩其他游戏机多消耗2%的能量。研究指出，该游戏并不能替代实际运动，但可能有助於控制体重。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/health/7155342.stm|title=Wii players need to exercise too|publisher=BBC News|date=2007-12-21|accessdate=2008-02-08|language=en|archive-date=2008-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081201035153/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/health/7155342.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>《Wii Sports》现已用於[[物理治疗|物理治疗]]加拿大Glenrose康复医院的一名拳击手，美国明尼蘇達州[[明尼阿波利斯|明尼阿波利斯]]和北卡罗来纳州[[罗利_(北卡罗来纳州)|罗利]]等地的中风患者，以及美国华盛顿、亞利桑那州[[普雷斯科特_(亚利桑那州)|普雷斯科特]]和德国[[兰德斯|兰德斯]]的受伤士兵。<ref>{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100204130423/http://www.cbc.ca/canada/edmonton/story/2007/05/11/wii-therapy.html|archivedate=2010-02-04|3=|url=http://www.cbc.ca/canada/edmonton/story/2007/05/11/wii-therapy.html|title=Wii-habilitation has Edmonton patients on their toes|publisher=Canadian Broadcasting Corporation|date=2007-05-11|accessdate=2008-02-08|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ArmyRehab">{{cite web|url=http://www.joystiq.com/2007/10/01/therapists-army-tap-wii-for-patient-rehab/|title=Therapists, Army tap Wii for patient rehab|publisher=Joystiq|first=Jason|last=Dobson|date=2007-10-01|accessdate=2008-02-08|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090728043901/http://www.joystiq.com/2007/10/01/therapists-army-tap-wii-for-patient-rehab/|archive-date=2009-07-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Wiihabilitate">{{cite web | url = http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/23070190/wid/11915829 | title = Break a leg? Try ‘Wiihabilitation’ | publisher = msnbc.com | date = 2008-02-08 | last = Tanner | first = Lindsey | accessdate = 2008-03-17 | language = en | archive-date = 2012-11-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121103120621/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/23070190/wid/11915829 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dcourier.com/main.asp?SectionID=1&SubSectionID=1&ArticleID=52318&TM=86342.05 |title=VA hospital employs video game as exercise aid |first=Derek |last=Meurer |publisher=The Daily Courier |date=2008-02-07 |accessdate=2008-02-10 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110709004142/http://www.dcourier.com/main.asp?SectionID=1&SubSectionID=1&ArticleID=52318&TM=86342.05 |archivedate=2011-07-09 }}</ref>

自从Wii发售之後，玩家在玩《Wii Sports》及其他游戏时受伤的情况就时有发生。玩家在挥动Wii手柄时可能会不小心打到其他玩家或物体，或者将手柄甩出去。<ref name="ABC-Video1" />在《Wii Sports》游戏过程中出现的一连串事故迫使任天堂社长[[岩田聪|岩田聪]]责成展开研究，以减少类似问题的发生。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.1up.com/do/newsStory?cId=3155722 |title=Iwata: We Are Investigating Wii Strap Issues |publisher=1UP.com |author=Klepek, Patrick |date=2006-12-07 |accessdate=2008-02-01 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120530114936/http://www.1up.com/do/newsStory?cId=3155722 |archivedate=2012-05-30 }}</ref>对於这一问题，任天堂发言人皆川恭广表示：“大家似乎兴奋了点儿，尤其是在玩《Wii Sports》的时候，因而有时手柄会从他们手中松脱。”2006年，任天堂回应称将召回320万Wii手柄腕带，并生产两倍厚的新腕带。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Technology/story?id=2727000&page=1|title=Snapping Wii Straps Force Major Recall, but Sales Bustling|publisher=ABC News|last=Silverstein|first=Jonathan|date=2006-12-15|accessdate=2008-02-02|language=en|archive-date=2022-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220109164543/https://abcnews.go.com/Technology/story?id=2727000&page=1}}</ref>

《Wii Sports》已然成为社交聚会和比赛的流行手段。在美国，老年中心和养老院的居民组成了《Wii Sports》保龄球联赛。<ref name="Seniors" /><ref name="RetireBowling">{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081011212809/http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/local/chi-070216nintendo%2C1%2C609357.story |archivedate=2008-10-11 |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/local/chi-070216nintendo,1,609357.story |title=Wii bowling knocks over retirement home |last=Wischnowsky |first=Dave |publisher=芝加哥論壇報 |date=2007-02-16 |accessdate=2008-02-08 |language=en |deadurl=yes }}</ref>游戏在澳大利亚发行後，任天堂和澳大利亚的连锁商场Myer公司共同於2007年1月在[[墨尔本|墨尔本]]举办了《Wii Sports》网球赛。<ref name="TennisTourn" />获胜者拥有与职业网球手[[柏·卡殊|帕特·卡什]]和[[马克·伍德福德|马克·伍德福德]]竞技的机会，并获得了全新的Wii作为奖品。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/757/757260p1.html|title=Wii Tennis Showdown AU|last=Shea|first=Cam|publisher=IGN|date=2007-01-21|accessdate=2008-02-01|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080214043626/http://wii.ign.com/articles/757/757260p1.html|archive-date=2008-02-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>美国纽约[[布鲁克林区|布鲁克林区]]的Barcade酒吧也曾在2007年6月23日举办过在一场名为“Wii布尔登”（Wiimbledon）的非官方《Wii Sports》网球赛，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gothamist.com/2007/06/19/lane_buschel_st.php|title=Lane Buschel & Steve Bryant, Wiimbledon Organizers|last=Mao|first=Tien|publisher=Gothamist|date=2007-06-19|accessdate=2008-01-31|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080224164425/http://gothamist.com/2007/06/19/lane_buschel_st.php|archivedate=2008-02-24}}</ref>比赛吸引了128名选手参加，其中不少人还身着游戏人物服装。比赛冠军赢得了一台全新的Wii。<ref name="ABC-Video1" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.abcnews.go.com/Technology/story?id=3310660&page=1|title=Bear Suit Guy Falls Short at 'Wiimbledon'|accessdate=2007-12-31|last=Hartenstein|first=Meena|date=2007-06-24|publisher=ABC News|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220429010523/https://abcnews.go.com/Technology/story?id=3310660&page=1}}</ref>

《Wii Sports》亦时常在电视上露面。游戏经常现身於Wii的各式广告，<ref name="WiiCommercial" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://wii.nintendo.com/wiicommercials_index.jsp |title=Wii Commercials — Wii Would Like to Play |publisher=任天堂 |accessdate=2008-02-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080129094913/http://wii.nintendo.com/wiicommercials_index.jsp |archivedate=2008-01-29 |language=en |deadurl=yes }}</ref>以及[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司（ABC）]]和[[國家廣播公司|全国广播公司（NBC）]]电视台的新闻节目中。<ref name="ABC-Video1" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.joystiq.com/2007/01/22/todays-healthiest-video-wii-sports-experiment-on-nbc/|title=Today's healthiest video: Wii Sports experiment on NBC|publisher=Joystiq|first=Ross|last=Miller|date=2007-01-22|accessdate=2008-02-08|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080328144553/http://www.joystiq.com/2007/01/22/todays-healthiest-video-wii-sports-experiment-on-nbc/|archive-date=2008-03-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web| url = http://kotaku.com/362590/today-show-gets-around-to-its-old-people-like-wii-story| title = Today Show Gets Around To Its "Old People Like Wii" Story| publisher = Kotaku| accessdate = 2008-03-10| language = en| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080304143756/http://kotaku.com/362590/today-show-gets-around-to-its-old-people-like-wii-story| archive-date = 2008-03-04| dead-url = yes}}</ref>在各色[[晚间娱乐节目|娱乐节目]]中也能屡屡觅得游戏的身影。美国[[談話節目|脱口秀]]节目《[[柯南·奥布赖恩深夜秀|柯南·奥布赖恩深夜秀]]》（''Late Night with Conan O'Brien''）的某集中，主持人柯南·奥布赖恩和嘉宾网球明星[[塞雷娜·威廉姆斯|小威廉姆斯]]打起了《Wii Sports》网球。<ref name="Conan" />而在加拿大的《Rick Mercer Report》节目裡，前加拿大[[总理|总理]][[让·克雷蒂安|让·克雷蒂安]]在《Wii Sports》拳击中击败了主持人Rick Mercer。<ref name="Mercer" />拳击游戏同样出现在了《科尔伯特报告》中，在其节目片段裡，主持人史蒂芬·科尔伯特和[[美國眾議院議長|美国众议院议长]][[蘭希·佩洛西|南希·佩洛西]]的Mii版造型在拳击场上一决雌雄。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.joystiq.com/2006/11/28/colbert-knocks-out-pelosi-in-wii-sports-boxing/|title=Colbert knocks out Pelosi in Wii Sports: Boxing|publisher=Joystiq|first=Kyle|last=Orland|date=2006-11-28|accessdate=2008-02-08|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080501144543/http://www.joystiq.com/2006/11/28/colbert-knocks-out-pelosi-in-wii-sports-boxing/|archive-date=2008-05-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>在[[第80屆奧斯卡金像獎|第80屆奧斯卡金像獎]]颁奖典礼上，主持人[[喬恩·史都華|乔恩·斯图尔特]]和《[[八月迷情|八月迷情]]》（''August Rush''）中的童星[[嘉米娅·西蒙娜·纳什|嘉米娅·西蒙娜·纳什]]（Jamia Simone Nash）更是在广告休息之後用舞台大屏幕大玩《Wii Sports》网球，利用这一笑点把观众拉回到颁奖现场。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.joystiq.com/2008/02/25/wii-tennis-makes-surprise-appearance-at-the-oscars/|title=Wii Tennis makes surprise appearance at the Oscars|publisher=Joystiq|first=Scott Jon|last=Siegel|date=2008-02-25|accessdate=2008-02-25|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080226071230/http://www.joystiq.com/2008/02/25/wii-tennis-makes-surprise-appearance-at-the-oscars/|archive-date=2008-02-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

